{"tid":1342144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"727光復元朗方略","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:16:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T18:00:37.000Z","uid":149773,"like":93,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"1810a6ec3635671deebf2257d3e5bf1e410f7916","tid":1342144,"uid":149773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:16:44.000Z","msg":"拆祠堂呢啲係最低消費<br />\n佢地今次行動無非都係想要錢<br />\n咁我哋除咗搞佢祠堂外<br />\n當然要搞埋佢陀地嘅鋪頭<br />\n做咗少少research<br />\n發現良田村係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新義安</span>地頭<br />\n而同樂街有大量雞竇<br />\n相信有部份都係佢地收陀地<br />\n另外發現元朗八鄉元崗村<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">泓利置業</span>都疑似係同佢地有關<br />\n<br />\n唔熟元朗 但想出一分力<br />\n希望元朗嘅朋友可以提供更多資訊<br />\n玩殘呢班鄉黑<br />\n黑警唔做嘢就我哋自己做<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"f40111223983dc844aeca0c9ec8aad5788efbf1a","tid":1342144,"uid":149773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:17:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a68db72079cc620de32e1454f03d97b175f502c","tid":1342144,"uid":149773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29937daf2d522aac9261e2e6e622dffd66f24e6d","tid":1342144,"uid":149773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i